urrently holds the best promise for measuring the magnetic field\nproperties of a large number of dwarf stars. [abridged]\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Mar 2006 21:00:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
